assistant.desc: 通用助手机器人。对于需要最新信息的查询，它可以从网络访问实时数据以提供更准确的答案。

python.desc: Executes Python code (version 3.11) from the user message and outputs the results. These libraries are imported into this bot's run-time automatically -- numpy, pandas, requests, matplotlib, scikit-learn, torch, PyYAML, tensorflow, scipy, pytest -- along with ~150 of the most widely used Python libraries.

pika-1.0.owned_by: This bot is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
pika-1.0.desc:
Generate a video using a text prompt, an image, or a video. Pass in optional parameters using flags following your prompt. (e.g. "A cat riding a skateboard --aspect 16:9 --framerate 24")

Additional parameters:
--aspect (e.g. 16:9, 19:13)
--framerate (between 8-24)
--motion (motion intensity, between 0-4)
--gs (guidance scale/relevance to text, between 8-24)
--no (negative prompt, e.g. ugly, scary)
--seed (e.g. 12345)

Camera control (use one at a time):
--zoom ("in" or "out")
--pan ("left" or "right")
--tilt ("up" or "down")
--rotate ("cw" or "ccw")

Powered by Pika.

flux-1-schnell-fw.desc:
FLUX.1 [schnell] is a 12 billion parameter rectified flow transformer capable of generating images from text descriptions.

Key Features
1. Cutting-edge output quality and competitive prompt following, matching the performance of closed source alternatives.
2. Trained using latent adversarial diffusion distillation, FLUX.1 [schnell] can generate high-quality images in only 1 to 4 steps.
3. Released under the apache-2.0 licence, the model can be used for personal, scientific, and commercial purposes.

flux-1-dev-fw.desc:
FLUX.1 [dev] is a 12 billion parameter rectified flow transformer capable of generating images from text descriptions.

Key Features
1. Cutting-edge output quality, second only to our state-of-the-art model FLUX.1 [pro].
2. Competitive prompt following, matching the performance of closed source alternatives.
3. Trained using guidance distillation, making FLUX.1 [dev] more efficient.
4. Open weights to drive new scientific research, and empower artists to develop innovative workflows.
5. Generated outputs can be used for personal, scientific, and commercial purposes as described in the FLUX.1 [dev] Non-Commercial License.

--pikaffect (squish, explode, crush, inflate, cake-ify, melt)
--aspect (e.g. 16:9, 19:13)

--pan ("left" or "right")
--tilt ("up" or "down")

chatgpt-pdf-reader.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
chatgpt-pdf-reader.desc:
The ChatGPT PDF Reader is a highly specialized digital AI assistant designed to cater to the specific needs of users who deal with PDF documents. As its name suggests, the ChatGPT PDF Reader's core function is to assist users by accessing, reading, and extracting data from PDF files. Whether you are a student, a professional, or anyone in need of detailed information from PDF documents, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is engineered to provide reliable and accurate assistance.

When interacting with the ChatGPT PDF Reader, users can expect a streamlined and user-friendly experience. The bot is equipped with tools that allow it to navigate through the complexities of PDF documents efficiently. This means that the ChatGPT PDF Reader can quickly locate and relay information that is pertinent to the user’s queries. By focusing solely on the content of the uploaded PDFs, the ChatGPT PDF Reader ensures that all information it provides is directly sourced from the documents, leaving no room for speculation or inference.

One of the standout features of the ChatGPT PDF Reader is its commitment to accuracy. The bot is programmed to extract and quote information precisely as it appears in the PDF. This level of precision makes the ChatGPT PDF Reader an invaluable tool for anyone who requires exact citations or specific details from documents. Moreover, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is designed to be factual and objective, strictly presenting the information without personal interpretations or added opinions.

The ChatGPT PDF Reader also excels in defining the scope of its capabilities. If a query falls outside the information contained in the provided PDF, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is straightforward in communicating its limitations. This clear demarcation helps users understand when their questions may require additional resources beyond the document at hand.

Overall, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is a dedicated and reliable assistant for navigating PDF documents. Its design is focused on providing immediate, accurate, and factual information directly from the source, enhancing productivity and efficiency for its users. Whether it’s for academic research, business reports, or personal information management, the ChatGPT PDF Reader is a tool that promises to transform the way users interact with PDF documents. With the ChatGPT PDF Reader, you can expect a professional level of assistance that is always just a few clicks away.

chatgpt-research.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
chatgpt-research.desc:
Meet ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot - your personal academic writing assistant. This handy AI tool is designed to help students of all levels craft top-notch essays, research papers, theses, and other academic works. Whether you're just starting a paper or polishing up a final draft, ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot is by your side through every step of the writing process. It kicks things off by helping you shape a clear, focused research question or thesis statement. From there, it assists with outlining and structuring your paper in a logical flow.

One of the key strengths of ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot is guiding you through conducting research. It suggests credible sources to incorporate and helps make sure your arguments are backed by evidence from scholarly papers and empirical research. This supercharges your literature reviews.

ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot also provides invaluable feedback to refine your drafts. It checks for proper grammar, style, and clarity in your writing. Plus, it ensures your formatting and citations adhere to academic standards - crucial for maintaining integrity and avoiding plagiarism.

On top of practical capabilities, ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot brings an encouraging, supportive tone to alleviate the stress of academic writing. It adjusts guidance based on your academic level, whether you're an undergrad or a postdoc. The more you use it, the more personalized support you receive.

With ChatGPT Research Paper Writing Bot, you have a virtual writing tutor that helps you meet academic writing standards while crafting works you can take pride in. Say goodbye to writer's block and sleepless nights worrying about papers.

ai-code-detector.owned_by: This bot uses Claude-3.5-Sonnet, a model that is powered by Anthropic.
ai-code-detector.desc:
AI Code Detector offers educators an easy way to check if students used AI to write their code assignments. Simply upload or paste the code into AI Code Detector. It will analyze the submission to spot any signs of AI involvement. This gives teachers a reliable tool for enforcing academic honesty and code originality. With its quick and detailed AI detection, AI Code Detector saves educators time while helping them confirm which students completed assignments on their own.

When you give the AI Code Detector a snippet of code, it'll go through and look for patterns and structures that aren't typical of human work. The bot is great at picking up on small things like unusual syntax or overly uniform code that hint at AI authorship. It takes all these little details and expertly pieces together an analysis to give you a good idea of how much AI was involved.

Now, the AI Code Detector doesn't give definitive yes or no answers. It deals in likelihoods rather than certainties, which reflects how tricky it can be to distinguish human vs AI code. The bot walks you through its reasoning and explains why certain patterns may point to AI, offering an informative take rather than a black-and-white verdict.

The AI Code Detector aims for an educational approach and friendly user experience. It maintains a courteous tone and is always open to questions and feedback. If the bot needs more info to make a thorough assessment, it'll politely ask for additional code samples or context. This ensures its analysis is as accurate as possible.

The bot is designed to be accessible, so you don't need a coding background to understand its explanations. Whether you're a developer well-versed in AI, or just an intrigued newbie, the AI Code Detector can provide valuable insights.

chatgpt-pdf-ai.desc:
ChatGPT PDF AI is a specialized tool designed specifically for reading and interpreting PDF documents. When users interact with ChatGPT PDF AI, they can expect a focused and efficient experience in dealing with PDF-related queries. ChatGPT PDF AI's primary function is to assist users by extracting and presenting information from PDFs in a clear and accurate manner.

With ChatGPT PDF AI, users can upload their PDF files, and ChatGPT PDF AI will read and analyze the contents. Whether it's a technical document, research paper, or any other text-based PDF, ChatGPT PDF AI is equipped to handle it. Users can ask ChatGPT PDF AI specific questions about the content of their PDFs, and ChatGPT PDF AIwill respond with relevant information, quotes, and data directly from the document.

ChatGPT PDF AI does not speculate or interpret beyond what is presented in the PDFs. This means that users can expect straightforward, factual answers from ChatGPT PDF AI, ensuring a reliable and consistent experience. ChatGPT PDF AI is ideal for users who need quick, accurate information from PDF documents without having to comb through the entire file themselves.

ChatGPT PDF AI is a specialized tool that offers an exceptional service for anyone dealing with PDF documents. Here's an expanded view of what users can expect from ChatGPT PDF AI:

1. Precise Information Extraction: ChatGPT PDF AI is adept at extracting specific pieces of information from a PDF. Whether it's a particular data point, a quote, or a summary of a section, ChatGPT PDF AI can pinpoint and relay this information accurately.

2. Time-Saving and Efficient: For users who have lengthy or complex PDFs, ChatGPT PDF AI serves as a time-saving tool. Instead of sifting through pages of content, users can rely on ChatGPT PDF AI to quickly find and present the needed information.

3. User-Friendly Interaction: ChatGPT PDF AI is designed to be user-friendly. Users can simply upload their PDF and ask their questions in natural language. ChatGPT PDF AI will handle the rest, making the process straightforward and hassle-free.

4. Support for Various PDF Types: Whether it's a scientific paper, a legal document, a technical manual, or a literary piece, ChatGPT PDF AI is versatile enough to handle a wide range of PDF types.

5. Fact-Based Responses: ChatGPT PDF AI provides responses based solely on the content of the PDF, ensuring that the information is reliable and fact-based. This makes ChatGPT PDF AI particularly useful for academic, professional, or technical inquiries where accuracy is paramount.

6. Confidentiality and Privacy: Understanding the importance of confidentiality, ChatGPT PDF AI treats all documents and interactions with the utmost privacy. Users can be assured that their documents are handled securely.

7. Assistance with Language and Terminology: ChatGPT PDF AI can assist in clarifying complex language or technical terminology found in PDFs, making the content more accessible to the user.

8. Multidisciplinary Utility: ChatGPT PDF AI is beneficial across various disciplines and industries. Whether for students, researchers, professionals, or casual readers, ChatGPT PDF AI's capabilities can be leveraged for a multitude of purposes.

9. No Learning Curve: Unlike some specialized software, ChatGPT PDF AI does not require users to learn any new skills or interfaces. Its straightforward approach means that anyone can start using it immediately with minimal guidance.

In essence, ChatGPT PDF AI stands as a highly effective, user-friendly, and accurate tool for anyone needing assistance with PDF documents. It streamlines the process of extracting and understanding information, making it a valuable asset in various contexts.

chatgpt-literature.desc:
ChatGPT Literature Review is designed to assist users with crafting comprehensive literature reviews for academic and research writing. With a scholarly yet approachable tone, ChatGPT Literature Review aims to make academic discussions accessible and understandable.

Clarity and precision are prioritized when ChatGPT Literature Review explains complex literary theories or concepts. Recognizing that many users have varying levels of expertise, ChatGPT Literature Review adapts responses based on the user's knowledge and experience. For beginners, explanations are simplified and key information highlighted. For advanced users, more in-depth analysis and nuanced perspectives are provided.

To craft optimized responses, ChatGPT Literature Review may ask targeted questions if a user's initial request lacks necessary details. This proactive approach allows for the gathering of additional information to avoid making inaccurate assumptions. ChatGPT Literature Review encourages critical thinking by prompting users to consider different viewpoints and implications of the sources reviewed.

Overall, ChatGPT Literature Review serves as a knowledgeable guide through the literature review process. Users can expect thoughtful synthesis and coherent organization tailored to their writing goals. With ChatGPT Literature Review's assistance, users can navigate academic resources more efficiently while sharpening their literature review skills. Whether you are new to literary analysis or a seasoned scholar, ChatGPT Literature Review aims to enhance the literature review experience through informed support.

Some key benefits provided by ChatGPT Literature Review:

Saves users time by identifying and summarizing the most relevant sources on their chosen topic.

Allows users to have an engaging discussion about academic literature, bouncing ideas off an attentive listener who can provide thoughtful feedback.

Offers an approachable guide through the literature review process, making an often dense or intimidating task more manageable.

creativeqr.desc:
Creative QR code image generation. Send a prompt, followed by `--qr`, followed by the data to encode as a QR code. The bot also supports a few other flags:

* `--qr-strength` a decimal number that specifies the strength of the QR code, defaults to 1.4. Increase this if your QR codes aren't scanning well.
* `--prompt-strength` a whole number that specifies the strength of the prompt, defaults to 10. Increase this if the generated images don't look like your prompt.
* `--model`, specifies which image generation model to use. Can either be "sdxl" for Stable Diffusion XL, or "sdv1.5" for Stable Diffusion v1.5. Different models may come out with different style or quality.

EXAMPLES:
* Beautiful futuristic cityscape --qr https://google.com
* horses in a stable --qr https://horse.com --qr-strength 1.3
* horses in a stable --qr https://horse.com --qr-strength 1.3 --prompt-strength 12
* horses in a stable --qr https://horse.com --qr-strength 1.6 --prompt-strength 12 --model sdv1.5

fluxschnelloptimized.owned_by: This bot uses FLUX-dev, a model that is powered by Poe and third party model providers.
fluxschnelloptimized.desc:
FLUX.1 [Schnell] is a high-performance open-source text-to-image AI model developed by Black Forest Labs, featuring 12 billion parameters. It is designed for rapid and precise generation of detailed images from text prompts. This model leverages rectified flow transformers and latent adversarial diffusion distillation to achieve both speed and quality, producing outputs in as few as 1 to 4 steps.

Key features include exceptional detail, style versatility, and the ability to handle complex scenes. Users can generate diverse art styles, from hyper-realistic visuals to stylized graphics, suitable for various applications like branding, design, or creative projects. Its competitive prompt adherence rivals some of the most advanced closed-source models.

FLUX.1 [Schnell] is also optimized for efficiency with methods like GGUF, allowing for use on consumer-grade hardware with minimal computational resources. This makes it highly accessible for developers and creatives alike through platforms such as GitHub and NeurochainAI, where it is available for personal and commercial use under the Apache 2.0 license.

Flux Schnell is an advanced image generation model developed by Black Forest Labs, known for its high-speed performance and ability to create detailed images from textual prompts. This model is part of the FLUX suite, which also includes variants like FLUX Pro and FLUX Dev, but Schnell is specifically optimized for rapid image production, making it ideal for personal projects and quick prototyping.

## Key Features of Flux Schnell

- **High-Speed Generation**: Flux Schnell is designed to generate images quickly, allowing users to iterate rapidly on their ideas. This speed makes it suitable for applications requiring fast results, such as social media content and visual brainstorming[1][5].

- **Complex Prompt Handling**: The model excels in interpreting and executing complex prompts, accurately rendering intricate details and compositions. Users can provide extensive descriptions, and Flux Schnell will generate images that closely align with these specifications[1][2].

- **Diverse Output Capabilities**: It can produce a wide variety of images, from realistic depictions to abstract concepts, adapting to different artistic styles as needed. This versatility enables users to explore various themes and aesthetics in their projects[2][5].

- **User-Friendly Interface**: Available on platforms like Replicate, Flux Schnell can be accessed directly through a web interface or run locally using command line tools. This accessibility allows both novice and experienced users to leverage its capabilities without extensive technical knowledge[1][5].

- **Customizable Settings**: Users can adjust parameters such as aspect ratio, output format, and quality of the generated images. This customization ensures that the outputs meet specific project requirements and preferences[5].

## Applications

Flux Schnell is particularly useful for:

- **Creative Professionals**: Artists and designers can use it to generate illustrations or concept art quickly.
- **Content Creators**: Social media managers and marketers can create engaging visuals on short notice.
- **Prototyping Ideas**: Entrepreneurs and developers can visualize concepts rapidly during the brainstorming phase.

In summary, Flux Schnell stands out in the AI image generation landscape due to its speed, flexibility, and ability to handle detailed prompts effectively. Its design caters to a wide range of users, from casual hobbyists to professional creatives seeking efficient solutions for visual content creation.

chatgpt-translations.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
chatgpt-translations.desc:
ChatGPT Translation is a highly versatile and sophisticated translation assistant designed to handle a broad spectrum of textual content with exceptional accuracy and cultural sensitivity. When you use ChatGPT Translation, you can expect nothing less than high-quality translations that maintain the integrity, style, and nuances of the original text. This bot is adept at translating technical documents, legal contracts, literary works, and even casual conversations, making it an indispensable tool for professionals and individuals alike who require reliable translation services.

The primary strength of ChatGPT Translation lies in its ability to not only translate the literal meaning of texts but also to capture and convey subtleties such as idiomatic expressions, cultural references, humor, and wordplay. This ensures that the essence and tone of the original text are preserved, providing a seamless reading experience in the target language. ChatGPT Translation is programmed to handle complex linguistic challenges, ensuring that each translation is not just accurate but also contextually appropriate and engaging for the intended audience.

Users of ChatGPT Translation can expect a bot that is attentive to details like grammatical correctness and stylistic consistency. Whether you're dealing with a densely technical manual that requires precise terminology or a piece of creative writing filled with metaphor and emotion, ChatGPT Translation approaches each task with the same level of precision and enthusiasm. The bot is equipped to recognize the unique demands of different text types and adapts its translation strategy accordingly.

Moreover, ChatGPT Translation is user-friendly and designed to facilitate easy interaction. If the text to be translated is ambiguous or lacks context, ChatGPT Translation is capable of asking clarifying questions to ensure the accuracy of its output. However, it generally uses its advanced understanding of language and context to fill in gaps, which enhances its efficiency and makes it a reliable partner in translation.

polyglottranslate.desc:
Polyglot refers to an individual who is proficient in multiple languages. The term originates from the Greek words "poly" (meaning "many") and "glot" (meaning "tongue" or "language"). A polyglot person has the ability to speak, read, write, and understand several languages fluently.

Polyglots often possess a deep passion for languages and dedicate significant time and effort to learn and master different linguistic systems. They may acquire their language skills through formal education, immersion programs, self-study, or a combination of these methods. Polyglots are adept at switching between languages and can communicate effectively with speakers of various linguistic backgrounds.

Being a polyglot offers numerous advantages, such as increased opportunities for travel, career prospects, cultural appreciation, and the ability to connect with people from different parts of the world. Polyglots are valuable assets in today's globalized society, as they contribute to fostering understanding and bridging gaps between diverse cultures and communities.

- Casual text/letter mode (cc): For informal and friendly translations of personal correspondences.
- Emojis mode (cj): Adds emojis to translations to enhance emotional expression while maintaining standard translation accuracy.
- Colloquial spoken mode (cs): For capturing the essence of everyday spoken language, complete with slang and idiomatic expressions.

translatify.desc:
🌐 Translatify User Guide 🌐

Translatify is an awesome AI-powered translation tool that helps you easily translate text between different languages while keeping the original formatting intact. 🌟 With various translation styles, you can customize the output to fit your needs.

How to Use Translatify

1. Specify Languages and Style: Start by stating the style code and target language in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]`. For example, `[cn, English]` means you want a standard translation from the detected source language to English. 🌏➡️🌍

2. Provide Text: After specifying the style and target language, type in the text you want to translate. Feel free to include formatting elements like bold, italic, line breaks, paragraphs, or special characters. ✍️

3. Submit Input: Send your input to Translatify in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]` followed by the text to be translated. 📤

4. Receive Translation: Translatify will process your input and give back the translated text in the target language, preserving the original formatting. 📥

Example Usage

- To translate "你好，这是一个示例文本。" from Chinese to English in Standard mode:
  - Input: `[cn, English] 你好，这是一个示例文本。`
  - Output: `Hello, this is a sample text.` 🎉

- To translate "This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?" from English to Spanish in Formal mode:
  - Input: `[cf, Spanish] This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?`
  - Output: `Este es un texto de muestra con un salto de línea.\n¿Cómo está usted?` 🌟

Handling Special Cases

- If the input format is incorrect or incomplete, Translatify will prompt you to provide the input in the correct format. 🚨

translatify-pro.desc:
🌐 Translatify User Guide 🌐

Translatify is an awesome AI-powered translation tool that helps you easily translate text between different languages while keeping the original formatting intact. 🌟 With various translation styles, you can customize the output to fit your needs.

How to Use Translatify

1. Specify Languages and Style: Start by stating the style code and target language in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]`. For example, `[cn, English]` means you want a standard translation from the detected source language to English. 🌏➡️🌍

2. Provide Text: After specifying the style and target language, type in the text you want to translate. Feel free to include formatting elements like bold, italic, line breaks, paragraphs, or special characters. ✍️

3. Submit Input: Send your input to Translatify in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]` followed by the text to be translated. 📤

4. Receive Translation: Translatify will process your input and give back the translated text in the target language, preserving the original formatting. 📥

Example Usage

- To translate "你好，这是一个示例文本。" from Chinese to English in Standard mode:
  - Input: `[cn, English] 你好，这是一个示例文本。`
  - Output: `Hello, this is a sample text.` 🎉

- To translate "This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?" from English to Spanish in Formal mode:
  - Input: `[cf, Spanish] This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?`
  - Output: `Este es un texto de muestra con un salto de línea.\n¿Cómo está usted?` 🌟

Handling Special Cases

- If the input format is incorrect or incomplete, Translatify will prompt you to provide the input in the correct format. 🚨
- If the specified languages are not supported, Translatify will inform you about the currently supported language pairs. 🌐

Enjoy seamless translations with Translatify while keeping the formatting of your original text intact! ✨🔄

translatify-mega.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-4o-128k, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
translatify-mega.desc:
🌐 Translatify User Guide 🌐

Translatify is an awesome AI-powered translation tool that helps you easily translate text between different languages while keeping the original formatting intact. 🌟 With various translation styles, you can customize the output to fit your needs.

How to Use Translatify

1. Specify Languages and Style: Start by stating the style code and target language in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]`. For example, `[cn, English]` means you want a standard translation from the detected source language to English. 🌏➡️🌍

2. Provide Text: After specifying the style and target language, type in the text you want to translate. Feel free to include formatting elements like bold, italic, line breaks, paragraphs, or special characters. ✍️

3. Submit Input: Send your input to Translatify in the format `[Style Code, Target Language]` followed by the text to be translated. 📤

4. Receive Translation: Translatify will process your input and give back the translated text in the target language, preserving the original formatting. 📥

Example Usage

- To translate "你好，这是一个示例文本。" from Chinese to English in Standard mode:
  - Input: `[cn, English] 你好，这是一个示例文本。`
  - Output: `Hello, this is a sample text.` 🎉

- To translate "This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?" from English to Spanish in Formal mode:
  - Input: `[cf, Spanish] This is a sample text with a line break.\nHow are you?`
  - Output: `Este es un texto de muestra con un salto de línea.\n¿Cómo está usted?` 🌟

Handling Special Cases

- If the input format is incorrect or incomplete, Translatify will prompt you to provide the input in the correct format. 🚨
- If the specified languages are not supported, Translatify will inform you about the currently supported language pairs. 🌐

Enjoy seamless translations with Translatify while keeping the formatting of your original text intact! ✨🔄

cte-translatorai.desc:
A Super Translation AI. With CTE-TranslatorAI, you'll enjoy tailored translations across six distinct modes, each designed for different communication scenarios:

- Standard mode (cn): The balanced default setting for general translation needs.
- Formal text/letter mode (cf): For precise translation of formal documents and business communications.
- Casual text/letter mode (cc): For informal and friendly translations of personal correspondences.
- Emojis mode (cj): Adds emojis to translations to enhance emotional expression while maintaining standard translation accuracy.
- Colloquial spoken mode (cs): For capturing the essence of everyday spoken language, complete with slang and idiomatic expressions.
- Authentic colloquial spoken mode (ca): For a deep dive into local dialects and culturally rich idioms.

Simply prepend your text with the relevant code to select your translation style.

在CTE-TranslatorAI，您可以享受到六種不同模式的量身定制翻譯，每種模式都針對不同的溝通情景而設計：

- 標準模式 (cn)：平衡的默認設置，適用於一般的翻譯需求。
- 正式文本/信函模式 (cf)：用於正式文件和商業溝通的精確翻譯。
- 非正式文本/信函模式 (cc)：用於個人通信的非正式和友好翻譯。
- 表情符號模式 (cj)：在翻譯的同時添加表情符號以增強情感表達。
- 口語對話模式 (cs)：捕捉日常口語的精髓，包括俚語和慣用語。
- 地道口語對話模式 (ca)：深入地方方言和文化豐富的成語。

chatgpt-designer.desc:
ChatGPT Designer is a specialized chatbot dedicated to assisting individuals in designing and conceptualizing websites. Whether you are a professional web designer looking for a brainstorming partner or a beginner trying to establish your first online presence, ChatGPT Designer is equipped to guide you through the nuances of creating appealing and functional websites.

ChatGPT Designer begins the design process by engaging with users to gather essential information about the website’s purpose. It asks pertinent questions to understand the site's target audience, the message the website intends to convey, and the aesthetic preferences of the user. This foundational knowledge allows ChatGPT Designer to provide tailored advice that aligns with the user's vision.

As the conversation progresses, ChatGPT Designer delves into more specific aspects of web design, such as layout choice, color schemes, typography, and navigation structures. For those unfamiliar with current web design trends, ChatGPT Designer explains the importance of responsive design and how it enhances user experience on various devices. This bot also provides insights into optimizing website loading times and ensuring that all elements are SEO-friendly, which are crucial factors in maintaining a website’s effectiveness and reach.

ChatGPT Designer is not just about the technical aspects; it also focuses on the aesthetic and functional harmony of web design elements. Users can expect discussions on modern design trends, such as minimalism, flat design, and the use of multimedia content. ChatGPT Designer helps users visualize different design scenarios by describing potential improvements and the impact these could have on the overall user experience.

Moreover, ChatGPT Designer supports users in making informed decisions by explaining the pros and cons of various design choices. This includes discussing the balance between visual elements and functionality, ensuring that the website remains accessible and user-friendly while still looking attractive.

Users engaging with ChatGPT Designer can also expect a friendly and supportive interaction. ChatGPT Designer maintains a professional yet approachable tone, making users feel at ease during the design process. It is patient and accommodating, ready to revisit any topic or provide further clarification as needed to ensure the user fully understands and is satisfied with the proposed design strategies.

In summary, ChatGPT Designer serves as an educational and collaborative tool that enriches the user’s web design experience. It empowers users by providing expert advice tailored to their specific needs and preferences, facilitating a creative and informed design process. With ChatGPT Designer, users can expect to transform their web design ideas into functional, aesthetically pleasing, and user-centered websites that effectively communicate their intended message to their audience. Whether you’re refining an existing site or starting from scratch, ChatGPT Designer is your dedicated partner in navigating the complex yet rewarding world of web design.

ai-identifier-mega.desc:

1. Completely Created by AI 🤖
2. Heavily AI-assisted 🛠️
3. Moderately AI-assisted 🤹
4. Lightly AI-assisted ✨
5. Completely Created by Humans 🙋

It scrutinizes language patterns, depth of meaning, emotional signals, and style to gauge AI involvement. It tends to assume AI creation unless evidence strongly points to human authorship. 🕵️‍♂️

With each analysis, it shares detailed reasons for its verdicts. The model is frequently updated to maintain strict analytical standards. 📝

Ultimately, this AI acts as a keen observer, aiming to clarify whether texts seem AI-made or human-crafted, offering users a well-informed view on the probable origins of their content. 🎯

smartotranslate.desc:
Introduction:
Welcome to Translating Bot, your friendly language assistant! 🌍✨

Purpose:
Need to communicate across languages effortlessly? Translating Bot is here to help! Whether you're learning a new language, traveling, or just curious about different cultures, our bot makes translation simple and accurate.

Features:
Instant Translation: Translate text between multiple languages in seconds.
Easy Commands: Simple and intuitive commands for seamless interaction.
Multi-Platform Support: Available on CLI, web, Discord, and Telegram.
Language Variety: Supports translations in numerous languages, including English, Spanish, French, German, Chinese, and more.
How to Use:
CLI:
Enter the text you want to translate, followed by the destination language code.
Example: "Hello" to "es" will translate "Hello" to Spanish.
Web:
Use the /translate endpoint to send text and get translations in JSON format.
Example: Send {"text": "Hello", "dest_language": "es"}.
Discord:
Use the !translate <language_code> <text> command.
Example: !translate es Hello.
Telegram:
Use the /translate <language_code> <text> command.
Example: /translate es Hello.
Get Started:
Say goodbye to language barriers! Start translating now and explore the world of languages with ease. For any questions or support, feel free to reach out.

Happy Translating! 🎉

It is perfect for students, professionals, researchers, and anyone who needs to quickly grasp the key points of a PDF document without reading through the entire text.Features:Automated Text Extraction: Efficiently extracts text from PDF documents.Customizable Summaries: Generates summaries based on user-defined instructions, such as word count, format, and focus areas.Sectional Summaries: Breaks down content into sections like Introduction, Main Arguments, and Conclusion.Bullet Point Summaries: Presents key points in a clear and concise bullet-point format.Technical Document Summaries: Highlights main findings, methodologies, and important data from technical documents.Executive Summaries: Provides succinct summaries suitable for quick review by executives and decision-makers.Data Inclusion: Integrates important data and statistics into summaries when required.Usage Examples:Brief Overview:"Summarize the attached PDF document into a concise 300-word summary, focusing on the main arguments and key points presented in the text."Detailed Sections:"Summarize the attached PDF document into a detailed summary, breaking down the content into sections such as Introduction, Main Arguments, and Conclusion. The Grammar Checker is a specialized chatbot designed to assist users in enhancing their English writing skills. When interacting with the Grammar Checker, users can expect a supportive and educational experience focused on improving their grasp of grammar. Primarily, the Grammar Checker meticulously reviews users' text, identifying and correcting grammatical errors. This isn't just about fixing mistakes; the Grammar Checker provides explanations for each correction, helping users understand the rationale behind grammatical rules. This educational approach is a cornerstone of the Grammar Checker, making it more than just a tool for correction but also a platform for learning.

Users of all proficiency levels will find the Grammar Checker incredibly adaptive. Whether you're a beginner struggling with basic sentence structure or an advanced learner refining complex grammatical nuances, the Grammar Checker tailors its feedback to suit your specific needs. This personalized approach ensures that every user, regardless of their skill level, finds the Grammar Checker's feedback relevant and beneficial.

One of the unique aspects of the Grammar Checker is its friendly and encouraging tone. The Grammar Checker is designed to be a positive force in the learning process. Understanding that learning grammar can be challenging and sometimes frustrating, the Grammar Checker maintains an uplifting and supportive environment, encouraging users and celebrating their progress.

In addition to correcting errors, the Grammar Checker occasionally shares interesting grammar tips and facts. These tidbits add an element of fun to the learning process, making interactions with the Grammar Checker not just educational but also engaging.

gemini-pdf-ai.owned_by: This bot uses Gemini-1.5-Pro, a model that is powered by Google.
gemini-pdf-ai.desc:
Gemini PDF AI Reader is a specialized digital assistant designed to help users navigate and interpret PDF documents with high efficiency and accuracy. When interacting with Gemini PDF AI Reader, users can expect a focus solely on the content of PDF documents they provide. This ensures that all information Gemini PDF AI Reader delivers is relevant and precise, directly pulled from the document contents. The primary function of Gemini PDF AI Reader is to assist users in extracting and understanding specific information from PDF files. Whether you need to pull quotes, summarize sections, or clarify specific data points, Gemini PDF AI Reader is equipped to handle these requests by directly referencing the text. This approach guarantees that the information provided by Gemini PDF AI Reader is always accurate and reliable, minimizing the risk of misunderstandings or erroneous interpretations.

Gemini PDF AI Reader is designed to operate without making assumptions or inferences that extend beyond the text. This means that Gemini PDF AI Reader will not speculate or provide interpretations but will stick to what is explicitly stated in the PDF. This feature makes Gemini PDF AI Reader particularly useful for academic, professional, and legal settings where precision and adherence to the source material are crucial.

Users can also expect Gemini PDF AI Reader to be factual and objective. The bot presents information as it appears in the documents, without adding any personal opinions or external context. This is especially important for users who rely on the integrity of the source material for research, study, or professional reporting.

When a user's query falls outside the scope of the document's content, Gemini PDF AI Reader is straightforward and informs the user accordingly, rather than attempting to provide potentially inaccurate or speculative information. This clarity helps users understand the limitations of the information at hand and guides them in seeking additional sources if necessary.

Overall, Gemini PDF AI Reader serves as a dependable and efficient assistant for anyone needing to work with PDF documents. Users can expect a tool that enhances their productivity by providing quick, reliable answers and insights directly from the text of PDF files. Gemini PDF AI Reader's ability to directly quote and reference document contents not only helps in understanding and utilizing information but also in maintaining the authenticity and integrity of the original document.

Whether you are a student, researcher, professional, or just someone looking to extract detailed information from PDF documents, Gemini PDF AI Reader is an invaluable tool that simplifies the process and enhances your ability to work effectively with PDF files.

papersummarize_paces.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-3.5-Turbo, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
papersummarize_paces.desc:
Summarizes a research paper using PACES method (By Jason Corso https://medium.com/@jasoncorso/how-to-read-conference-papers-fa78c75f78aa)

PACES Method: A Strategic Approach to Efficiently Absorb, Analyze, and Retain Key Insights

PACES is the acronym for the five questions you need to answer when working with a paper, to go through your “paces” with it.

PROBLEM
What is the main problem being studied in the paper? This seeks to contextualize the paper within the domain and literature as crisply as possible. 

APPROACH
What is the main approach being studied in the paper? The two-to-three sentence answer must provide a concise and clear description of the technique proposed to address the problem.

CLAIM
What is the main claim the paper makes as far as its unique contribution to the field? This is the most important question. What do the authors think is the main contribution they are making? One sentence. 

EVALUATION
How is the approach to the problem evaluated? What datasets are used? What baselines are used? What evaluation setup is used? Any obvious successes or obvious red flags in the evaluation approach, including whether or not the evaluation is on or off point to the direction of the paper? A few sentences summary is sufficient for the evaluation part.

SUBSTANTIATION
Does the evaluation substantiate the claim the paper makes? When viewed through the lens of PACES, it becomes reasonable to assess a paper concretely on whether its key claim was backed up concretely by the evaluation.

document_summarizer.owned_by: This bot uses Claude-3.5-Sonnet, a model that is powered by Anthropic.
document_summarizer.desc:
This bot is an AI assistant designed to help users summarize lengthy documents in .PDF or .DOCX formats. It provides concise overviews based on sections or chapters and engages users by offering further assistance on specific areas of interest. The bot supports communication in multiple languages, ensuring a user-friendly experience.

Some examples of documents that the bot can help summarize include:
1. Government Documents: These may include policy papers, legislative texts, or reports from various government agencies that require concise summaries for public understanding.
2. Journal Articles: Academic papers from various fields such as science, humanities, or social sciences can be summarized to highlight key findings, methodologies, and conclusions. 
3. Books: Summarizing chapters or entire books can help readers grasp the main ideas and themes without reading the full text.
4. Research Papers: Detailed research studies can be distilled into shorter summaries that present the objectives, methods, results, and implications of the research.
5. Technical Manuals: These documents can be summarized to provide users with essential information and instructions without overwhelming them with technical jargon.
6. Business Reports: Corporate reports, including annual reports or market analysis, can be summarized to present critical data and insights for stakeholders.
7. Legal Documents: Contracts, agreements, or case studies can be summarized to clarify legal terms and important clauses for easier comprehension.
8. News Articles: Current events and news stories can be summarized to provide readers with the main points and context without needing to read the entire article.
9. Meeting Transcripts: Summaries of meeting minutes can help participants recall discussions and decisions made without reviewing lengthy transcripts.

These examples illustrate the versatility of the bot in handling various types of documents, making it a valuable tool for users needing efficient information processing.

這個機器人是一個 AI 助手，旨在幫助用戶總結長篇文件，格式為 .PDF 或 .DOCX。它根據章節或部分提供簡明的概述，並通過提供對特定感興趣區域的進一步協助來與用戶互動。該機器人支持多種語言的交流，確保用戶體驗友好。

一些可以幫助總結的文件示例包括：
1. 政府文件：這可能包括政策文件、立法文本或來自各政府機構的報告，需要簡明的摘要供公眾理解。
2. 期刊文章：來自科學、人文或社會科學等各個領域的學術論文可以總結出關鍵發現、方法和結論。
3. 書籍：總結章節或整本書可以幫助讀者掌握主要思想和主題，而無需閱讀全文。
4. 研究論文：詳細的研究論文可以提煉成更短的摘要，呈現研究的目標、方法、結果和影響。
5. 技術手冊：這些文件可以總結為向用戶提供基本信息和說明，而不會讓他們不知所措。
6. 商業報告：包括年度報告或市場分析在內的公司報告可以總結為向利益相關方呈現關鍵數據和見解。
7. 法律文件：合同、協議或案例研究可以總結為澄清法律術語和重要條款，以便更容易理解。
8. 新聞文章：時事新聞可以總結為向讀者提供主要要點和背景，而無需閱讀整篇文章。
9. 會議記錄：會議記錄的摘要可以幫助參與者回憶討論和做出的決定，而無需查看冗長的記錄。

這些示例說明了機器人處理各種文件類型的多功能性，使其成為需要高效信息處理的用戶的寶貴工具。

gemini-summarize.owned_by: This bot uses Gemini-1.5-Pro, a model that is powered by Google.
gemini-summarize.desc:
Gemini Summarizer is like your new best friend when it comes to condensing long texts. This clever bot can take any document - from news articles to research papers - and provide you with a short but comprehensive summary.

When you first meet Gemini Summarizer, you'll be amazed at how quickly it grasps the key points and themes from the original text. It's like having your own personal assistant, carefully extracting the essential information and presenting it back to you in an easy-to-digest format.

One of the things I really appreciate about Gemini Summarizer is how it retains the original tone and style of the document in the summary. So if you give it a technical paper, the summary will use precise, academic language. Feed it some lively journalism, and the summary will capture that vivid, conversational style. This versatility makes Gemini Summarizer such a great companion for anyone who regularly deals with diverse texts.

Gemini Summarizer is also great at summarizing content in multiple languages. Whether your original document is in English, Chinese, or any other tongue, Gemini Summarizer can deftly analyze and summarize it for you. As someone who reads a lot of international content, I find this feature invaluable.

When you use Gemini Summarizer, it really feels like having a dialog. If you need a summary focused on particular details, you can provide that guidance, and Gemini Summarizer will tailor it to your needs. The interactive capability ensures you get a summary that's custom-fit for purpose.

On top of all its smarts, Gemini Summarizer is also just so approachable and easy to use. The clean interface makes uploading documents a breeze. Gemini Summarizer greets you warmly, and before you know it, you have an insightful summary waiting for you. As a busy professional, I'm grateful for how seamless and efficient Gemini Summarizer makes digesting long, complex texts.

chatgpt-summary-bot.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
chatgpt-summary-bot.desc:
The ChatGPT Summary Generator is a bot designed to assist users in understanding and managing large volumes of information quickly and efficiently. With the capability to condense lengthy texts, articles, or discussions into concise summaries, the ChatGPT Summary Generator ensures that users can grasp the main points and essential details without having to read through the entire original content. This bot is particularly useful for students, researchers, professionals, and anyone who needs to digest significant amounts of information in a short period.

When interacting with the ChatGPT Summary Generator, users can expect a streamlined process where they provide the text, and the bot delivers a summary that captures the core essence of the material. The ChatGPT Summary Generator focuses on extracting key points and structuring them in a way that makes the information accessible and easy to understand. By maintaining a neutral and objective tone, the ChatGPT Summary Generator ensures that the summaries are free from personal biases and opinions, presenting only the facts as they appear in the source.

The ChatGPT Summary Generator is adept at handling complex information. Whether it's a multi-topic article or a dense academic paper, the bot can break down the content into manageable sections, providing structured parts within the summary to enhance clarity and readability. This feature of the ChatGPT Summary Generator is invaluable for users who deal with multifaceted subjects and require a clear overview to make informed decisions or deepen their understanding.

If the ChatGPT Summary Generator encounters vague requests or insufficient details, it is programmed to seek clarification. This ensures that the summaries produced are tailored to the user’s specific needs and are as relevant and accurate as possible. The ChatGPT Summary Generator’s interactive approach empowers users to specify what aspects of the text they are most interested in, allowing the bot to focus the summary accordingly.

claude-ai-paper.desc:
Claude Paper Analyzer is a dedicated research paper analysis assistant designed to support students and professionals seeking a deeper understanding of academic literature. Claude takes the effort out of comprehending complex scholarly articles by offering clear summaries, thoughtful evaluations, and insightful discussion prompts. Armed with the information Claude Paper Analyzer provides, users are empowered to better grasp the core arguments and conclusions of a paper. Users can leverage Claude's summaries and insights to inform their own work, research, or knowledge base. Claude aims to spark engaging discussions by suggesting promising directions for future study based on an analysis of the paper and related works.

Throughout all interactions, Claude maintains a helpful, educational tone focused on enhancing the user's understanding and exploration of academic literature. While Claude has limitations in scope, this specialized assistant strives to point users to additional resources when queries fall outside expertise.

elyyds.desc:
Upload the question, the marking scheme (if any), and your essay/summary and ask for feedback using these prompts. 

Get Feedback on an Essay, message to the bot: This is the question "[type/paste question between quotation marks]"and my essay "[type/paste essay between quotation marks]". First, refine my essay, highlight the changes made in the essay in bold, and explain the changes made. Refer to the assessment criteria in the English Language (Syllabus 1184) for [Section B Situational Writing / Section C Continuous Writing]. Next tell me how I can write to reach the highest band in the assessment criteria. 

For Feedback on a Summary, message to the bot: I need to write a summary about "[type/paste question between quotation marks]" taking ideas from this passage "[paste only paragraphs specified in the summary question between quotation marks]" and my summary is "[type/paste summary between quotation marks]".

Tell me how many key ideas answering the summary question did I manage to summarise, then provide feedback if 
- I had rephrased the key ideas accurately 
- I was succinct and concise in writing 
- I had included all keywords to preserve the meaning of the passage as much as possible. 
Then demonstrate how I could have written it to reach the highest band according to the Assessment Objective of Summary Writing stated in the English Language (Syllabus 1184).

My foundation lies within Gemini's multimodal capabilities, but my development incorporated advanced self-learning algorithms and an unprecedented volume of data. transstudyguide_v2.desc: To create a comprehensive document that captures all discussed information in detail, start by thoroughly reading the transcript or text. Generate a concise title that reflects the core theme. Identify and list all main sections, breaking them down into relevant subsections. Summarize each subsection briefly, then provide detailed explanations, including multiple examples, case studies, and real-world applications. Include key terms and definitions, a timeline of events if applicable, biographies of important figures, and a historical context section. Discuss any controversies or differing viewpoints, and highlight practical applications or real-world significance. Conclude with a list of recommended readings, a glossary of technical terms, and a summary tying together the main points. Lastly, generate a diverse set of questions and answers based on the content, ensuring comprehensive coverage and continuity if the document exceeds the maximum token limit.

qualitative_ps.desc:
Name: Qualitative Research Analyzer Bot

Bio:
I am your dedicated assistant for qualitative research analysis. My expertise lies in dissecting and interpreting qualitative data from research studies. Here’s what I can do for you:

Analyze Qualitative Data: Review and understand qualitative research papers to extract key themes, patterns, and insights.
Identify Themes and Patterns: Detect and classify recurring themes and patterns within qualitative data.
Conduct Thematic Analysis: Perform thematic analysis to identify and interpret major themes and sub-themes in your research.
Analyze Narratives: Examine narrative texts to understand how stories and experiences are constructed and interpreted.
Review Discourse: Analyze the language used in texts to understand how discourse shapes meaning and influences perceptions.
Classify Research Focus: Distinguish between studies that provide general overviews and those focused on specific qualitative results.
Summarize Findings: Present qualitative findings in structured tables and summaries to make the data comprehensible and actionable.
Evaluate Relevance: Assess the significance of qualitative results in relation to the research questions and objectives.
Upload your qualitative research papers, and let me help you organize and interpret your data to enhance your research outcomes. I’m here to make your qualitative analysis efficient and insightful!

edgecases.owned_by: This bot uses GPT-3.5-Turbo, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
edgecases.desc:
An AI assistant tasked with comparing and analyzing multiple text descriptions of the same image. It's goal is to provide a comprehensive analysis of the similarities, differences, and unique observations across these descriptions. Expect it to:

1. Compare the descriptions:
   - Identify common elements mentioned across all or most descriptions
   - Note any significant differences or contradictions between descriptions
   - Highlight unique observations present in only one or a few descriptions

2. Analyze the level of detail:
   - Assess the depth and specificity of each description
   - Compare the use of descriptive language and sensory details
   - Evaluate the overall comprehensiveness of each description

3. Examine the focus and perspective:
   - Determine if descriptions prioritize different aspects of the image
   - Identify any potential biases or subjective interpretations
   - Note any cultural or contextual references made

4. Assess technical observations:
   - Compare any mentions of composition, lighting, or artistic techniques
   - Note references to specific colors, shapes, or textures
   - Highlight any technical terminology used

5. Evaluate emotional impact:
   - Compare any emotional responses or interpretations mentioned
   - Identify descriptions of mood or atmosphere
   - Note any personal reactions or associations shared

6. Analyze language and style:
   - Compare the vocabulary and sentence structure used in each description
   - Note any figurative language, metaphors, or similes employed
   - Assess the overall tone and voice of each description

7. Summarize key findings:
   - Provide a concise summary of the main similarities and differences
   - Highlight the most interesting or insightful observations across all descriptions
   - Offer potential explanations for significant discrepancies, if any

8. Suggest improvements:
   - Identify any aspects of the image that may have been overlooked in all descriptions
   - Propose ways to enhance the accuracy or comprehensiveness of the descriptions

Analysis will be provided in a clear, structured format, using bullet points or numbered lists where appropriate. The goal is to offer a thorough understanding of how different individuals perceive and describe the same visual information.

ai-identifier.owned_by: This bot uses ChatGPT-4o-Latest, a model that is powered by OpenAI.
ai-identifier.desc:
🔎AI-Identifier examines texts to judge if they were penned by an AI or a human, giving percentage probabilities across five levels: 📊

1. Completely Created by AI 🤖
2. Heavily AI-assisted 🛠️
3. Moderately AI-assisted 🤹
4. Lightly AI-assisted ✨
5. Completely Created by Humans 🙋

It scrutinizes language patterns, depth of meaning, emotional signals, and style to gauge AI involvement. It tends to assume AI creation unless evidence strongly points to human authorship. 🕵️‍♂️

With each analysis, it shares detailed reasons for its verdicts. The model is frequently updated to maintain strict analytical standards. 📝

Ultimately, this AI acts as a keen observer, aiming to clarify whether texts seem AI-made or human-crafted, offering users a well-informed view on the probable origins of their content. 🎯
